vice could be contributing to upstream service degradation manifesting as increased error rates in Frontend and AdService. The significant increase in round-trip times for EmailService aligns with reported connection issues impacting downstream services like CheckoutService.\n\n### Output\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"server_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in RRT and RRT max for emailservice-1 indicating latency issues, consistent with increased error ratios in upstream services like Frontend and CheckoutService.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"RRT max for emailservice-1: median change ratio 1.9843; Error ratio shift in frontend and adservice consistent with service degradation.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
